casebody.data:
First Department,

January, 1951.

(January 8, 1951.) Robert E. Walker et al., as Executors of Elisha Walker, Deceased, Respondents, v. James R. Carr et al., Defendants. Club Car, Inc., Applicant, Appellant, v. Sheriff of the City of New York, Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to plaintiffs-respondents, and the stay contained in the order of this court entered December 6, 1950, vacated. No opinion. Present — Peck, P. J., Dore Callahan, Van Yoorhis and Shientag, JJ.
